           \n\n<div class=\"kksr-legend\" style=\"font-size: 19.2px;\">\n            5\/5 - (93 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #d83131;\">GIA S\u01af LUY\u1ec6N IELTS &#8211; CHUY\u00caN LUY\u1ec6N THI IELTS, CAM K\u1ebeT CH\u1ea4T L\u01af\u1ee2NG\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd H\u1eccC TH\u1eec N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC VI\u00caN KH\u00d4NG H\u00c0I L\u00d2NG<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">Hotline: <span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 110%;\"><b>0962.005.996<\/b><\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><strong>GIA S\u01af TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T &#8211; CUNG C\u1ea4P GIA S\u01af CHUY\u00caN LUY\u1ec6N IELTS<span style=\"color: #d83131;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> gi\u1ecfi chuy\u00ean luy\u1ec7n thi IELTS 1:1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eeb <strong>FRE-IELTS<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>IELTS MASTER<\/strong> <span style=\"color: #000000;\">t\u1ea1i TP.H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\/ TP.HCM v\u00e0 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">&#8220;<em>d\u1ea1y online&#8221;<\/em><\/span>\u00a0 to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 IELTS<\/strong> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfng Anh uy t\u00edn tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u. C\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 IELTS v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m cao s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c, vi\u1ec7c <strong>h\u1ecdc IELTS 1 k\u00e8m 1 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n thi IELTS<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c luy\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<div class=\"s-block-item s-repeatable-item s-block-sortable-item s-blog-post-section blog-section\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"sixteen columns\">\n<div class=\"s-blog-section-inner\">\n<div class=\"s-component s-text\">\n<div class=\"\">\n<div class=\"s-component-content s-font-heading\">\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"I_GIA_SU_LUYEN_IELTS_1_1_PHU_HOP_VOI_AI\"><\/span><span class=\"#(className)\" style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>I. GIA S\u01af LUY\u1ec6N IELTS 1:1 PH\u00d9 H\u1ee2P V\u1edaI AI?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"input_line_0\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 IELTS\">B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 IELTS<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"input_line_1\"><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"color: #000000;\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee8ng tuy\u1ec3n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u00ean, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, \u0110i du h\u1ecdc, \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 ho\u1eb7c Th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng IELTS...\">B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee8ng tuy\u1ec3n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u00ean, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc, \u0110i du h\u1ecdc, \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 ho\u1eb7c Th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng IELTS&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"input_line_2\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n\">B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian \u00f4n luy\u1ec7n<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"input_line_3\"><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"color: #000000;\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian. \">B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian. <\/span><\/li>\n<li id=\"input_line_4\"><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"color: #000000;\" data-mention=\"Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n IELTS nhanh t\u1eeb 2 \u2013 3 th\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 IELTS n\u1eefa.\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n IELTS nhanh t\u1eeb 2 \u2013 3 th\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 IELTS n\u1eefa.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"input_line_5\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a, d\u1ea1y nhanh &amp; ch\u1ea5m b\u00e0i nhanh - L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh tinh g\u1ecdn\">B\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a, d\u1ea1y nhanh &amp; ch\u1ea5m b\u00e0i nhanh &#8211; L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh tinh g\u1ecdn<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"input_line_6\"><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"color: #000000;\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 band \u0111i\u1ec3m IELTS trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t.\">B\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 band \u0111i\u1ec3m IELTS trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li id=\"input_line_7\"><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"color: #000000;\" data-mention=\"L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh l\u1edbp C\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c Gia s\u01b0 IELTS 1 k\u00e8m 1 tinh g\u1ecdn, target band 6.5-7.0-8.0 sau 2-3-4 th\u00e1ng (tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean)=\">L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh l\u1edbp C\u1ea5p t\u1ed1c Gia s\u01b0 IELTS 1 k\u00e8m 1 tinh g\u1ecdn, target band 6.5-7.0-8.0 sau 2-3-4 th\u00e1ng (tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean)=<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"input_line_8\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean band\">B\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean band<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li id=\"input_line_10\"><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"color: #000000;\" data-mention=\"H\u1ecdc vi\u00ean d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng band \u0111i\u1ec3m nhanh ch\u00f3ng\">H\u1ecdc vi\u00ean d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng band \u0111i\u1ec3m nhanh ch\u00f3ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li id=\"input_line_11\"><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"color: #000000;\" data-mention=\"B\u1ea1n y\u1ebfu 1 trong 4 k\u0129 n\u0103ng IELTS v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng band nhanh k\u0129 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y\">B\u1ea1n y\u1ebfu 1 trong 4 k\u0129 n\u0103ng WRITING &#8211; SPEAKING &#8211; LISTENING &#8211; READING v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng band nhanh k\u0129 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"input_line_14\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\" data-mention=\"=&gt;&gt;&gt; Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y ielts t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\/ online ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 cao, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.\">=&gt;&gt;&gt; <strong>Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong> cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y ielts t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\/ online ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 cao, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/em><\/span><\/div>\n<div id=\"input_line_15\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em>&gt;&gt; Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi <strong>Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong> ngay h\u00f4m nay theo s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: <strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0962.005.996<\/span> <\/strong>ho\u1eb7c<strong> <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0987.005.996<\/span><\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n!<\/em><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"II_%E2%80%93_LOI_ICH_HOC_GIA_SU_IELTS_1_1\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>II &#8211; L\u1ee2I \u00cdCH H\u1eccC GIA S\u01af IELTS 1:1<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian:<\/strong> Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian \u0111i l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>H\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: <\/strong>Gi\u00e1o \u00e1n d\u1ea1y <strong>C\u00c1 NH\u00c2N H\u00d3A<\/strong> cho t\u1eebng h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi gia s\u01b0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c nhanh h\u01a1n, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Linh ho\u1ea1t: <\/strong>B\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ecbch h\u1ecdc, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cao: <\/strong>Gia s\u01b0 s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft, chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u t\u1eebng k\u0129 n\u0103ng<strong> WRITING &#8211; SPEAKING\u00a0 &#8211; LISTENING\u00a0 &#8211; READING<\/strong>\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: <\/strong>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft gia s\u01b0 chuy\u00ean ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef, \u0111\u00fang chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 s\u01b0 ph\u1ea1m v\u1eefng, h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 minh b\u1ea1ch, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"p3\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><em>==&gt;&gt; <strong>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u00ed do tr\u00ean, gia s\u01b0 LUY\u1ec6N ILETS 1:1 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ed1 1 v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n. <\/strong><\/em><\/span><i><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em>&gt;&gt; Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi <strong>Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong> ngay h\u00f4m nay theo s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: <strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0962.005.996<\/span> <\/strong>ho\u1eb7c<strong> <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0987.005.996<\/span><\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 t\u00ecm gia s\u01b0 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n!<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"III_%E2%80%93_DOI_NGU_LUYEN_IELTS_GIOI\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>III &#8211; \u0110\u1ed8I NG\u0168 LUY\u1ec6N IELTS GI\u1eceI?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 Luy\u1ec7n IELTS<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>B\u1eaeT BU\u1ed8C <\/strong>\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean, Th\u1ea7y c\u00f4 Gi\u00e1o Vi\u00ean, Gi\u1ea3ng Vi\u00ean <strong>GI\u1eceI TOP <\/strong>\u0111\u1ea7u<strong> t\u1ea1i<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Gia_su_la_Giao_vien_Giang_Vien\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>?<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, Gi\u1ea3ng Vi\u00ean:<\/strong><\/span><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, Gi\u1ea3ng vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110H TOP \u0111\u1ea7u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf danh ti\u1ebfng, \u0111ang tham gia gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y Ti\u1ebfng Anh t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110H tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\/ Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf. C\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 IELTS 8.0+, <\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng l\u1edbp luy\u1ec7n thi IELTS t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c Trung T\u00e2m c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng chuy\u00ean Luy\u1ec7n IELTS.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">Tr\u00ean 5 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m luy\u1ec7n thi, n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc c\u1ea7u tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ec1 thi, b\u1ed9 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ec1 thi phong ph\u00fa, b\u00e1m s\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Gia_su_la_Sinh_vien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><strong>? Gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 Sinh vi\u00ean:<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">L\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean khoa Ti\u1ebfng Anh, Chuy\u00ean Anh c\u1ee7a \u0110H Ngo\u1ea1i Ng\u1eef, \u0110H H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, Ngo\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u01a1ng, S\u01b0 Ph\u1ea1m Anh, Ngo\u1ea1i Giao&#8230; c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ielts t\u1eeb 7.0+, t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea1t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch h\u1ecdc sinh gi\u1ecfi t\u1ec9nh, qu\u1ed1c gia.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">L\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean gi\u1ecfi, c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc \u0110H, c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m thi \u0110H m\u00f4n Ti\u1ebfng Anh t\u1eeb 9+<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y ielts<\/strong> nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m gia s\u01b0 ielts, n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc c\u1ea7u tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ec1 thi, b\u1ed9 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ec1 thi phong ph\u00fa, b\u00e1m s\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3835 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/GSBM-QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-603.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/GSBM-QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-603.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/GSBM-QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-603-300x201.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/GSBM-QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-603-768x515.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><em style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">? H\u1ecdc 1 k\u00e8m 1 gi\u00fap gia s\u01b0 &amp; h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nhau hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"IV_%E2%80%93_HOC_PHI_GIA_SU_LUYEN_IELTS\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24; font-size: 100%;\"><strong>IV &#8211; H\u1eccC PH\u00cd GIA S\u01af LUY\u1ec6N IELTS<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #000000;\"><i style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #555555;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3831 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Gia-SU-IELTS.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Gia-SU-IELTS.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Gia-SU-IELTS-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/Gia-SU-IELTS-768x512.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><br \/>\n<\/i><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 <strong><em><span style=\"color: #282828;\">h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed d\u1ea1y online\/ t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/span><\/em><\/strong> tham kh\u1ea3o. H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1ecdi chi ti\u1ebft xin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 <em><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0962.005.996<\/span> <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">ho\u1eb7c<\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0987.005.996<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/em>\u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_CHINH_SACH_HOC_THU\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 105%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #33cccc;\">? <\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">CH\u00cdNH S\u00c1CH H\u1eccC TH\u1eec<\/span><\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/strong>\u00a0s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u: Trong \u0111\u00f3 gia s\u01b0 l\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 hai bu\u1ed5i, v\u1edbi Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc sinh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p d\u1ea1y, gi\u00e1o \u00e1n, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 2 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc th\u1eed nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3812 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm.png 900w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-300x201.png 300w, https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/QUY-DINH-HOC-THU-900-x-600-mm-900-x-600-mm-768x515.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"V_%E2%80%93_CAM_KET_CUA_TRUNG_TAM_GIA_SU_TRI_VIET\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>V &#8211; CAM K\u1ebeT C\u1ee6A TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">Cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0<strong> MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd &#8211; \u0110\u00daNG &amp; CHU\u1ea8N<\/strong>\u00a0theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 th\u00f4ng tin r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ee9ng minh th\u01b0 &amp; th\u1ebb sinh vi\u00ean, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean trong bu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ea1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">T\u00ecm v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i gia s\u01b0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u00a0<strong>MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd<\/strong>.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>Gia s\u01b0 <strong>NGHI\u00caM T\u00daC<\/strong> trong c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>T\u1eadn t\u00e2m, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 d\u1ea1y h\u1ebft b\u00e0i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft gi\u1edd.<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\"><b><i><\/i><\/b>D\u1ea1y \u0111\u00fang ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00fang y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecdc sinh &amp; gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 105%;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 24\/7 tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong>?\u00a0<\/strong>V\u1edbi 12 n\u0103m trong d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cung c\u1ea5p gia s\u01b0, s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u01a1n 15.000+ gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi, trung t\u00e2m gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gia s\u01b0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"font-size: 105%; color: #000000;\"><em><strong>?\u00a0<\/strong>G\u1ecdi ngay Hotline: <strong><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0962.005.996<\/span> <\/strong>ho\u1eb7c<strong> <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0987.005.996<\/span><\/strong>\u00a0ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n 24\/7 m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><\/h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CONG_TY_TNHH_TRI_VIET_VIET_NAM_%E2%80%93_TRUNG_TAM_TRI_VIET\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>TRUNG T\u00c2M GIA S\u01af TR\u00cd VI\u1ec6T<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em>? V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng 1: 40 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u00fd Ki\u00ean, C\u1ea7u Gi\u1ea5y, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em>? V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng 2: 125 M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh, Nam T\u1eeb Li\u00eam, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em>? V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng 3: S\u1ed1 263 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh, ph\u01b0\u1eddng Xu\u00e2n H\u00f2a, t\u1ec9nh Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd, Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em>\u260e\ufe0f Hotline: <strong><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0962.005.996<\/span> <\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">ho\u1eb7c<\/span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">0987.005.996<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em>? Website: https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"p2\">\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GIA S\u01af LUY\u1ec6N IELTS &#8211; CHUY\u00caN LUY\u1ec6N THI IELTS, CAM K\u1ebeT CH\u1ea4T L\u01af\u1ee2NG\u00a0 D\u1ea0Y TH\u1eec 02 BU\u1ed4I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd 100% H\u1eccC PH\u00cd H\u1eccC TH\u1eec N\u1ebeU H\u1eccC VI\u00caN KH\u00d4NG [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1655,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[492],"tags":[128,130,129,127,126],"class_list":["post-928","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-gia-su-tieng-anh-mb","tag-gia-su-day-ielts","tag-gia-su-day-kem-ielts","tag-gia-su-ielts-tai-nha-ha-noi","tag-gia-su-luyen-thi-ielts-tai-nha","tag-gia-su-luyen-thi-ielts-tai-nha-ha-noi"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n thi ielts t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 - C\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ielts 8.0 - Gia s\u01b0 Tr\u00ed Vi\u1ec7t<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y k\u00e8m, luy\u1ec7n thi IELTS t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Gia s\u01b0 gi\u1ecfi Ti\u1ebfng anh c\u00f3 IELTS 8.0+, h\u1ecdc th\u1eed 2 bu\u1ed5i. Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 nhanh\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/giasubinhminh.com\/gia-su-luyen-day-thi-ielts-co-chung-chi-ielts-8-0-cam-ket-chat-luong\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Gia s\u01b0 d\u1ea1y thi ielts \u2013 Gia s\u01b0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng ch\u1ec9 ielts 8.0 \u2013 Cam k\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"T\u1eeb A - Z b\u00ed k\u00edp v\u1ec1 gia s\u01b0 luy\u1ec7n thi IELTS t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 gia s\u01b0 v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 huynh kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua! \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u00ean c\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u